title: #229: Lisa Lisa (@Wayne Rada)
itunes:title: Lisa Lisa with Wayne Reda
description: Wayne Rada met me in NoLita, Manhattan to take me on a tour of the murals down there. It's a history of graffiti and a run-down of the giant, builiding sized paintings that are all over lower Manhattan.
